# Morphological Transducer for Purepecha

# Part of speech categories
# <n>      # Noun
# <v>      # Verb
# <adj>    # Adjective
# <obj>    # Object
# <det>    # Determinant
# <num>    # Number

# <sent>   # Sentence-ending punctuation
# <guio>   # Hyphen
# <cm>     # Comma
# <apos>   # Apostrophe
# <quot>   # Quotation mark
# <lquot>  # Left quotation mark
# <rquot>  # Right quotation mark
# <lpar>   # Left parenthesis
# <rpar>   # Right parenthesis

# Verbs
# <nom>    # nominalising suffix
# <agnt>   # nominalising suffix (agent)
# <p1>     # 1st person
# <p2>     # 2nd person
# <p3>     # 3rd person
# <past>   # past
# <pres>   # present
# <fut>    # future
# <cni>    # conditional
# <pri>    # present indicative
# <perf>   # perfect (aspect)
# <dur>    # duration (aspect)
# <hab>    # habitual (aspect)
# <incp>   # inceptive
# <itg>    # interrogative


# Number morphology
# <pl>  # Plural
# <sg>  # Singular

# Other symbols
# >      # Morpheme boundary

###############################################################################
###                       M O R P H O T A C T I C S                         ###
###############################################################################

PATTERNS
NounRoot RegNounInfl
ObjectRoot RegNounInfl Object
Adjective
Determiner [<det>:]
Number
Verbs
# V-Stem AspectTime ModeInterrogative
Punctuation


PATTERN Verbs
V-Stem(1) [<v>:] V-Stem(2): AspectTime ModeInterrogative
# V-Stem(1) [<v>:] V-Stem(3): ModeInterrogative

###############################################################################
###                          L E X I C O N                                  ###
###############################################################################

LEXICON RegNounInfl

<n><sg>:
<n><pl>:>echa

LEXICON Object

<obj>:>ni

LEXICON AspectTime

<pres><dur>:>xa
<pres><hab>:>sïn
<pres><perf>:>s
<pres><incp>:>xam
<past><dur>:>xap
<past><hab>:>sïam{M}
<past><perf>:>sp
<past><incp>:>xamam{M}
<cni>:>pirin
<fut>:>a

LEXICON ModeInterrogative

<p1><sg>:>kani
<p1><pl>:>ksï
<p2><sg>:>ri
<p2><pl>:>tsï
<p3><sg>:>ti
<p3><pl>:>ksï
<itg>:>{K}i
<p1>:>{K2}a
<p2>:>{K2}a        #ambiguity

